 race&#32;left&#32;right Runs two flows concurrently and returns the result of the first one to complete.
Remarks The &ldquo;loser&rdquo; flow is interrupted immediately.
Parameters left: Flow&lt;&lsquo;env, &rsquo;error, &lsquo;value&gt; right: Flow&lt;&lsquo;env, &rsquo;error, &lsquo;value&gt;

 zipPar&#32;left&#32;right Combines two flows into a tuple of their values, running them concurrently.
Remarks If either flow fails, the other is interrupted immediately.
Parameters left: Flow&lt;&lsquo;env, &rsquo;error, &lsquo;right&gt; right: Flow&lt;&lsquo;env, &rsquo;error, &lsquo;right&gt;
